==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: malacca cane
<hw>malacca cane</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <def>A walking
cane made from the stem of a species of palm of the genus
<gen>Calamus</gen> (<spn>Calamus Scipionum</spn>), and of a brown color,
often mottled. The plant is a native of Cochin China, Sumatra, and
Malays.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Malachite</ent>⟦br⟧
